Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:42.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:59.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:06.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:15.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.23,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請不要讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.48,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的觸碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.02,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 請不要對生命無愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.07,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}儘管這絕望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.74,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失準的時鐘 記錄著生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:33.62,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落滿地的記憶之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:37.50,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:42.47,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看 卻是那麼輕易
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.76,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:51.02,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.10,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}請不要讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.15,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的觸碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:59.65,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}為了不再失去曾經擁有的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:06.49,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}讓我忘卻自己的過去 重新開始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.70,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 請不要對生命無愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.79,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}儘管這絕望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:15.21,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願那讓你苦不堪言的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:20.80,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}會迎來完結的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:24.42,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我卻要目送你離開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.84,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們終將會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.89,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重來對新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:30.97,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.56,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們終將會重來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.73,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重來對新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.15,EDCNCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}與你攜手邁進
